getAccessType

public AccessType getAccessType()
Gets the access type. If the BeanPropertyDefinition has either a getter of a settter, then the access type depends on the accessors. If there is no accessor method set for this BeanPropertyDefinition, then the access type that was set with setAccessType(accessType) is returned.

Returns the access type
